meta {
  name: Documents
  seq: 1
}

docs {
  Endpoints for storing content that will later be retrieved by `/search`
  and `/ask`. Both endpoints generate embeddings via the configured
  `EmbeddingProvider` (Ollama `nomic-embed-text`, 768 dims, by default; or
  OpenAI `text-embedding-3-small` if `EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=openai`) and persist
  them to the `embeddings` table in Postgres/pgvector.
}
